{"lemma":"جِماحٌ","slug":"جِماحٌ","root":"ج.م.ح","root_slug":"ج-م-ح","root_link":"/words/roots/ج-م-ح","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":false},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n6245"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%AC%D9%90%D9%85%D8%A7%D8%AD%D9%8C"}},"translations":null,"definition":null,"etymology":null,"ipa":null,"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n6245","headword_ar":"جُمَّاحٌ","root":"jmH","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"An arrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, K,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a small arrow,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"without an iron point, having a round head, with which the art of shooting is learned"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L, K)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"by a boy:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, L:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"one with which boys play, putting upon its head a date or some clay, in order that it may not wound:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L:) or it signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a date put upon the head of a piece of wood, with which boys play:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"birds are shot at with it, and knocked down, without being killed, so that the shooter takes them:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it is also called"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jub~aAHN","text_ar":"جُبَّاحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":": (T, TA:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a boy's arrow, upon the end of which he puts a lump of chewed dates of the size of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EifaAD","text_ar":"عِفَاض"},{"kind":"text","text":"[here meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"stopper"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of a bottle, in order that it"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the end"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may go more directly, and be smooth; without feathers, and sometimes without a notch."},{"kind":"text","text":"(AHn, L.)       -A2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"That"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"kind of plant"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"at the extremities of which come forth what resemble ears of wheat, soft,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"like foxes' tails, or"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"resembling the heads of the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"HaliY~","text_ar":"حَلِىّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Sil~iyaAn","text_ar":"صِلِّيَان"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and the like:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(L, K:) a coll. gen. n.: n. un. with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"p","text_ar":"ة"},{"kind":"text","text":": (L:) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAmiyHu","text_ar":"جَمَامِيحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and in poetry"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamaAmiHu","text_ar":"جَمَامِحُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (L, K;) the latter allowable only in cases of necessity. (L.)       -A3-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"jamuwHN","text_ar":"جَمُوحٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"."}],"source_refs":["S","K","L","T","TA"]}]},"classical_definitions":null}